{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2512/comments/47279663.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2512#comment-47279663"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2512.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 2512, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Bug in URDF to SDF convertion for Boolean tags in Gazebo 9"}, "content": {"raw": "This problem appeared to me cos I used Gazebo9 with ROS kinetic.\nFor ROS melodic it is fixed in gazebo_ros_utils by comparing Integers and Booleand\n\n\n```\n#!c++\n\nif(boost::iequals(value, std::string(\"true\")) || boost::iequals(value, std::string(\"1\")))\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This problem appeared to me cos I used Gazebo9 with ROS kinetic.\nFor ROS melodic it is fixed in gazebo_ros_utils by comparing Integers and Booleand</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">boost</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">iequals</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">string</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;true&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">||</span> <span class=\"n\">boost</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">iequals</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">value</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">string</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;1&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)))</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-08-15T11:16:44.563201+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Petro Shmigelskyi", "uuid": "{6cfe95d8-117a-4c6d-9fff-99c8c634d56f}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B6cfe95d8-117a-4c6d-9fff-99c8c634d56f%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B6cfe95d8-117a-4c6d-9fff-99c8c634d56f%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/52d486fd5ae793cd33554ca348455c42d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsPS-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Petro Shmigelskyi", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e277558b-5860-4800-bc3d-58ef003ec447"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 47279663}